    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in fair condition. The interior shows visible wear on upholstery and trim, including staining and scuffing in high-contact areas. Controls and displays are functional. The exterior has noticeable scratches and minor dents consistent with regular use. Mechanically sound with no major issues reported.",
